    "en": {
      "title": "Three people who went swimming died; One is magic",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The police said that three of the four youths who went missing while swimming in a waterfall in Pitapetara area, Matara, were recovered as dead bodies today (27).",
        "A search operation has been launched by the navy but the search has been suspended due to shortage of kerosene and oxygen.",
        "Later, it is reported that the bodies were found only after a joint operation by the marines, police and local residents.",
        "Police said that 22, 23 and 24-year-old youths have died and a 24-year-old youth is missing."
      ],
